    "body": "## Problem\r\n`make_position_params`/`get_line_byte_from_position`/`make_line_range_params` are private functions,  and their functionality can be replaced by `vim.pos` now.\r\n\r\n## Solution\r\nRemove them, use `vim.pos` instead.\r\n",
    "closed_at": "2026-05-16T16:20:14Z",
