            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I simply moved `get_lines` from `util.lua` to `pos.lua`. After checking the git blame, it appears it was used this way from the very beginning without any specific justification. https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/c98e4d1a2ab700f563740c033abfc1fe1c955637",
            "commit_id": "a7f09db9de683f0bb1f4bc5725e39be63666b89c",
            "created_at": "2026-05-16T16:06:42Z",
